        {
            "title": "舜宇上月手機鏡頭與手機攝像模組出貨量按年均錄雙位數跌幅",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">舜宇光學(02382)公布，今年3月份手機鏡頭與手機攝像模組出貨量，按年均錄雙位數跌幅。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：舜宇光學官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/07/20230719_FI_source-web_02382.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：舜宇光學官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/07/20230719_FI_source-web_02382.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：舜宇光學官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">該公司解釋，出現上述情況，主要因為公司專注於中高端案子，且產品結構較去年同期改善所致。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">在3月份，舜宇光學的手機鏡頭出貨百9431.6萬件，按年跌16.3%，按月也減少2.9%；手機攝像模組出貨量3731.4萬件，按年跌10.9%，按月則提升5.5%。</p>\n\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"舜宇光學官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/02382-Web.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"舜宇光學官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/02382-Web.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">舜宇光學官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">期內車載鏡頭出貨量982.1萬件，按年升16.5%，按月也增11.5%，主要受惠客戶端需求提升；玻璃球面鏡片出貨量216.2萬件，按年升10.8%，按月大增65.5%；其他鏡頭出貨量695萬件，按年顯著增加61.1%，按月微升4.1%。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">至於手機攝像模組以外的其他光電產品上月出貨量，則為288.8萬件，按年降11.7%，按月升10.8%。顯微儀器出貨量2676.8萬件，按年及按月分別大升78.8%及46.4%。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/14844558-%e8%88%9c%e5%ae%87%e4%b8%8a%e6%9c%88%e6%89%8b%e6%a9%9f%e9%8f%a1%e9%a0%ad%e8%88%87%e6%89%8b%e6%a9%9f%e6%94%9d%e5%83%8f%e6%a8%a1%e7%b5%84%e5%87%ba%e8%b2%a8%e9%87%8f%e6%8c%89%e5%b9%b4%e5%9d%87%e9%8c%84",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/11/02382-Web2.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2025-04-10 16:45:38",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "全日收市｜港股全日升417點  銀行及汽車股午後上揚",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">港股全日收升417點，午後區間波動，京東健康(06618)午後飆升，本地銀行股及汽車股上揚。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"港股 AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20230808_FI_source-ap_港股12.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"港股 AP圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20230808_FI_source-ap_港股12.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">港股 AP圖片</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">恒生指數全日報20681點，升417點或2.06%，今早開市報20810點，升545點或2.69%，最高見21211，飆947點或4.67%，為全日高位，其後升幅大幅收窄，最低見20530，僅升266點或1.31%，為全日低位，午後區間波動。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">恒生科技指數全日報4813點，升124點或2.66%，今早開報4875點，升185點或3.96%；</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">恒生國企指數全日報7668，升132點或1.76%，今早以7719點開市，升183點或2.43%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">即月期指報20696點，升508點或2.52%，高水14點 ; 國指期貨報7668點，升132點或1.76%，低水5點 ; 科指期貨報4820，升149點或3.19%，高水6點。 </p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">大市全日成交3955.34億元。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">京東健康(06618)午後升幅擴大，收升8.15%，報32.5元，為表現最佳藍籌股。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">聯想(00992)升7.07%，報8.03元 ; 比亞迪電子(00285)升6.7%，報31.05元升幅居藍籌股二、三位 ; 舜宇光學(02382)升5.42%，報62.2元 ; 瑞聲科技(02018)升5.76%，報34.9元 ; 高偉電子(01415)報19.86元，揚3.98%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">本地銀行股升，滙控(00005)升5.58%，報75.7元，為支持大市主力 ; 恒生(00011)升3.04%，報96.65元 ; 中銀香港(02388)升2.66%，報28.9元。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">汽車股上揚，理想汽車(02015)升4.85%，報85.4元 ; 小鵬(09868)升4.4%，報71.2元 ; 比亞迪(01211)升2.69%，報344.2元 吉利(00175)升4.19%，報14.92元，成交俱入20大。’</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">小米(01810)升2.75%，報43.05元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">中國神華(01088)跌1.78%，報30.35元; 新東方(09901)跌0.89%，報33.6元 ; 新奧能源(02688)跌0.83%，報60元，三藍籌股表現最差。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/14844559-%e5%85%a8%e6%97%a5%e6%94%b6%e5%b8%82%ef%bd%9c%e6%b8%af%e8%82%a1%e5%85%a8%e6%97%a5%e5%8d%87417%e9%bb%9e-%e9%8a%80%e8%a1%8c%e5%8f%8a%e6%b1%bd%e8%bb%8a%e8%82%a1%e5%8d%88%e5%be%8c%e4%b8%8a%e6%8f%9a",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/20240415_FI_source-web_HKStock-1.png.webp",
            "pub_date": "2025-04-10 16:40:36",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "安德利果汁料首季純利按年升50%至70%",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">安德利果汁(02218)發盈喜，預期今年首季歸屬上市公司股東淨利潤8007萬元(人民幣．下同)至9087萬元，按年升50%至70%。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/20240411_fi_安德利果汁_source-web_官網_fb.png.webp\">\n<img src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/20240411_fi_安德利果汁_source-web_官網_fb.png.webp\"/>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">預計期內歸屬上市公司股東並扣除非經常性損益的淨利潤約7903萬至8983萬元，按年也增長32%至50%。該公司解釋，首季盈利提升，主要因為客戶訂單需求增加，濃綜果汁的銷售量按年大幅增長所致。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/14844517-%e5%ae%89%e5%be%b7%e5%88%a9%e6%9e%9c%e6%b1%81%e6%96%99%e9%a6%96%e5%ad%a3%e7%b4%94%e5%88%a9%e6%8c%89%e5%b9%b4%e5%8d%8750%e8%87%b370",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/20240411_FI_02218_source-web.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2025-04-10 16:30:40",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
